Robin Irvine https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robin_Irvine 0 Robin Irvine (21 December 1901, Stoke Newington, London, England – 28 April 1933, Bermuda) was a British film actor. He was married to actress Ursula Jeans from 1931 until his death. Robin_Irvine ( 21 December_1901 , Stoke_Newington , London , England – 28_April_1933 , Bermuda ) was a_British_film_actor .
